data.description: Tranquil Oasis with a Pond - Perfect for private Fishing and Relaxation!  Welcome to your own slice of paradise in Loganville's Wildwood at Meadow gate! This beautifully maintained 5-bedroom, 3-full bath residence offers not only a stunning home but also a serene backyard retreat. Behind the home, you'll discover a beautiful pond that adds a touch of nature's magic to your daily life. You can sit in your enclosed back patio to relax and unwind with stunning views of the back landscape. Walk into your open-concept layout that creates a seamless flow between the living spaces, providing ample room for entertainment and family gatherings. Spacious main-level master bedroom suite, offering privacy and easy accessibility. The main bath has his and her sinks, walk in closet, separate shower and new walk-in tub. There are 2 other bedrooms downstairs, which is great for an office and spare room while you also have an entire finished bonus upstairs with a full bath and 2 more bedrooms! So much space for a big family or growing family. Home has been meticulously taken care of, ensuring it's in pristine condition for its new owners. Benefit from newer HVAC, roof, and a tankless water heater, providing both comfort and energy efficiency. The neighborhood is packed with amenities including a pool, tennis courts and playground for the kids! Schedule a private showing today!
